name: Seabird observations along the coasts of Greenland, Iceland, Faeroes and the North East of Scotland (June-August 1974)
description: First part of dataset gives an overview of seabirdsobserved between 25 June and 31 July 1974 alongGreenland, Iceland, Faeroesand the North East of Scotland. The second part gives thebirding times for all stationswhereornithologicalobservations were made. Additionally air and water temperature measurements were noted for some stations. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Joiris, C.(1976). Seabirds seen during a return voyage fromBelgium to Greenland in July.
